articles.title: Influencer Andrew Tate can be extradited to the UK after Romanian trial - Al Jazeera English
articles.description: Tate and his brother Tristan were detained on Monday night on allegations of sexual aggression dating back to 2012-2015.
articles.content: A Romanian court has approved a request from the United Kingdom to extradite controversial influencer Andrew Tate but said it would postpone the extradition until his criminal trial in Romania had co… [+3308 chars]
